		|Дата,
		|MestoViyavleniya,
		|NarushennyeTrebovaniya,
		|Organizaciya,
		|OtvetstvenniyZaKachestvo,
		|PodrobnoeOpisanie,
		|Proekt,
		|VyyavivshayaOrganizaciya,
		|VyyavivsheePodrazdelenie,
		|VyyavivsheeLico", Истина);
	
